data.description: Well loved true split level in home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with 2 bonus rooms downstairs (perfect for a fourth bedroom conversion). Enjoy a large, spacious family room with plenty of natural light and a beautiful fireplace.   Flat, fenced in back yard on a large open lot. The eat-in kitchen is ideal for cozy dining and features a new backsplash. This home is sits in Douglasville's quiet Country Park neighborhood, on a quiet back street with no through traffic.
